      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Dr Eurig Scandrett (BSc, MSc, MPhil, PhD) is a Senior Lecturer in Sociology in the Psychology, Sociology and Education Division. He is a member of the <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/9e59330129ac41028d861633fdcb6a2d}" title="Centre for Applied Social Sciences">Centre for Applied Social Sciences</a>, Centre for Dialogue and Public Engagement and Public Sociology Research Group.</p>]]></Value>
